title: The Big Book of Vice (DC Comics) (1998) Pdf Gooner
description:
Publisher: DC Comics; First Edition edition (September 1, 1998)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 1563894548
ISBN-13: 978-1563894541

Written by Steve Vance and D.A. Stern; Art by various THE BIG BOOK OF VICE examines humanity's worst habits in all their sinful glory. Ranging from true acts of debauchery to harmless infatuations, this guilty pleasure exposes the negative aspects of alcohol, gambling, tobacco, prostitution, drugs, pornography, candy, pinball machines, comic books and video games. Also expanding its reach to touch on the dens of immorality and the greatest advocates of errant behavior, this comic-style book includes special features on Las Vegas, Sodom, Phoenix City, Larry Flynt, Carrie Nation, and Timothy Leary
